Add OTP SMS service and secure OTP verification
Implement a real SMS service for OTP delivery and secure the OTP verification process.
* **OTP Generation and Delivery**: - Replace the mock OTP sending function with Twilio integration in `app/api/auth/otp/route.ts`. - Add error handling for SMS service failures in the `POST` method. - Remove demo mode and ensure only valid OTPs are accepted in the `PUT` method.
* **User Registration**: - Update OTP generation and verification logic in `app/api/auth/register/route.ts`. - Remove demo user handling and ensure proper error handling for OTP-related operations.
* **User Login**: - Update OTP verification process in `app/api/login/route.ts` to work with the new OTP system. - Add error handling for OTP-related operations.
* **Auth Provider Component**: - Update `login` and `verifyOtp` methods in `components/auth-provider.tsx` to work with the new OTP system. - Add error handling for OTP-related operations.
